ank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-t%C3%AC-b%E1%BB%99-Ti%C3%AAu-lang-trung-th%E1%BA%ADp-huynh/poem-aB57mSvNVwdnkl12M3H0kw">Tặng tì bộ Tiêu lang trung thập huynh - 贈比部蕭郎中十兄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Vi-th%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1n-Thi%E1%BB%87n/poem-yLRKAkj2lh75AOUrMH64cw">Tặng Vi thất tán Thiện - 贈韋七贊善</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Kinh-Nam-thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-GrO2vAOFDwGICb-JExBRKA">Thu nhật Kinh Nam thuật hoài tam thập vận - 秋日荊南述懷三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-mai/poem-m60tKVQoonnoG6CkMWHQiw">Vịnh mai - 詠梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
